      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative comparison metric (e.g., E_rel) must be computed with uncertainty bounds; agreement within 15% of experimental hemolysis index required.",
      "rationale": "Relative error ranges from 18% to 42% across operating points when experimental uncertainty is propagated. Systematic over-prediction observed at high shear rates. Achieved level 2 against required level 4."
