      "acceptanceCriteria": "The power-law hemolysis damage model must be evaluated against alternative constitutive models (e.g., strain-based, mechanistic RBC models); model-form uncertainty must be quantified.",
      "rationale": "Only the Giersiepen-Wurzinger power-law model was used. No model-form uncertainty study comparing alternative hemolysis constitutive relations has been performed. This is the primary epistemic gap at MRL 5."
